Reverse an Array
You are given an array of integers arr[]. Your task is to reverse the given array.

Code:

class Solution {
    public void reverseArray(int arr[]) {
        int start = 0;
        int end = arr.length-1;
        while(start < end){
            int temp = arr[start];
            arr[start] = arr[end];
            arr[end] = temp;
            
            start++;
            end--;
        }
    }
}
Time Complexity: O(n)

Space Complexity: O(1)


